The man was allegedly found in possession of ID documents, covid-19 certificates, bank cards and other sensitive documents. eNCA's Pule Letshwiti-Jones reports. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - One suspect was arrested during an anti-crime operation in Hillbrow, Johannesburg. The man was allegedly found in possession of ID documents, covid-19 certificates, bank cards, and other sensitive documents. Police say they were responding to a tip-off and that the man appears to be acting alone. eNCA's Pule Letshwiti-Jones reports